OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 02 JUN
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1953FOn one of the coldest June days
OL,7,Fof the century, after 16 months of
OL,8,Fplanning, Princess Elizabeth is crowned
OL,9,FQueen Elizabeth II, in a ceremony at
OL,10,FWestminster Abbey.
OL,11,
OL,12,FThis would be the first televised
OL,13,FCoronation. BBC TV went on air earlier
OL,14,Fthan usual that day - at 9.15am -
OL,15,Fradiating the test card, to allow
OL,16,Fviewers more time to adjust their
OL,17,Faerials
OL,18,
OL,19,F20.4 million people watched at least
OL,20,Fhalf an hour of the service - almost
OL,21,Fdouble the radio audience. This was the
OL,22,Ffirst time the television audience
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
