OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1981FThe first edition of Razzmatazz
OL,7,Fairs on ITV. A music-based children's
OL,8,Fprogramme.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThe programme would run for nine
OL,11,Fseries, between 2nd June 1981 and 2nd
OL,12,FJanuary 1987. It was produced by Tyne
OL,13,FTees Television and initially featured
OL,14,Fpresenters Alastair Pirrie and Lyn
OL,15,FSpencer.
OL,16,
OL,17,FLater presenters included Brendan
OL,18,FHealy, Suzanne Dando and singer Lisa
OL,19,FStansfield, who joined the show when
OL,20,Fshe was 16.
OL,21,
OL,22,
